title: Starman's Quest
creator: Robert Silverberg
description: LibriVox recording of Starman's Quest, by Robert Silverberg. Read by Dawn Larsen. Travelling at speeds close to that of light, spacemen lived at an accelerated pace. When one of the twin boys left the starship, he grew older while his twin in space barely aged. So the starship twin left the ship to find what happened to his brother who was aging away on earth. (Summary by Bead Krazy Dawn) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
